name: v1.29.0
body:
## Changelog
### New Features
* c90086f26464141976ab300796714926858de2f1: feat: Added OTel Connectors (#1139) (@cpheps)
* 7cb4bf29e4b4a91d0bc1dfed06a939f800de6421: deps: Update OTel to [v0.81.0](https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-collector-contrib/releases/tag/v0.81.0) (#1142) (@cpheps)
  * Notable Features
    *  `filelogreceiver`: Add support for tracking the current file in filelogreceiver
    * `googlecloudexporter`: Adds an experimental, opt-in write ahead log for GCP metrics exporter.
    * `hostmetricsreceiver`: Add new Windows-exclusive process.handles metric.
  * Notable Bug Fixes
    * `windowseventlogreceiver`: Fix buffer overflow when ingesting large raw Events 
### Bug Fixes
* ff12b7cd47363f97fd4bebbda2f17c0f911be9e1: fix(install): Fixes Linux reinstallation after manual uninstall (#1138) (@cpheps)
* 59738a72fe9e2dbdd2a1ce420aa044fda38d3573: fix: Revamp M365 receiver (#1135) (@dpaasman00)
### Dependencies
* e86d79e1a9298bbc9859e585286afdfc76c8b823: deps(container): Replaced deprecated openjdk container image with eclipse-temurin (#1136) (@cpheps)
* 8864f69710b7dff2acf5763803b711a4f99254a0: deps: Dependabot 07-10-23 (#1146) (@cpheps)
* 79828595d5a180770bd1286aa22ba574c1298c73: deps: Upgrade mockery to v2.30.16 (#1133) (@antonblock)
